subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Who is known as the 'Khiladi' of Rajasthan?
question_hi: राजस्थान की किताब कौन से लोगों के रूप से 'खेलना' का नाम देते हुए कहा गया है।
explanation_en: Raja Man Singh I is known for being the General of Mughal Emperor Akbar and is famous for his strategic skills. He is also known as the "Khiladi" of Rajasthan.
